{"tid":2012334,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【英超回歸】英國政府開綠燈 批准6.1重開大型體育賽事","createTime":"2020-05-11T14:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T14:28:41.000Z","uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"57be2ed16538f252745a341316aa6f16b7703423","tid":2012334,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"繼首相約翰遜於周日就疫情發表全國性講話後，英國政府周一頒佈一份長達50頁紙的國家防疫措施鬆綁指引，其中重點標示為避免群眾聚集令病毒傳播，6月1日之前禁止國內所有職業體育及文娛活動以任何形式舉行及作直播。指引預示只要國內疫情持續穩定下，英超有望於下月復賽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200511&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=60928807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200511%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D60928807&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=d0882200\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200511%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D60928807&h=e7573ac3\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200511&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=60928807</a>"},{"pid":"fa83fe7bcdcde719ed73c2061ca50ad79b5f2c20","tid":2012334,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"01fd93d81d245997451c725f00bb511d34350fe8","tid":2012334,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"噚日先有球員確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}